                  </hi>. This is my husband's handkerchief—it was gone with the coats—it was found in the prisoner's pocket at the station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was cooking potatoes for you, and you went up stairs; I found you in a state of intoxication; they gave me the handkerchief. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> No, I did not.</p>
